<center><table border=0><tr><td><center><H2><font face=arial>Its not hard to roleplay on Rallos Zek! (txt)</font></H2></center>
<font face=arial size=2><b>Posted By:</b> <A HREF="/cgi-local/whois2.cgi?Rune">Rune</a><br>
<b>Posted On:</b> 1:51 p.m. 19/3/1999<br>
<b>Subject:</b> Its not hard to roleplay on Rallos Zek! (txt)<p>
<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/pvpquest/images/divider.gif" width=452 height=22 border=0></center><BR></STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#FFFFFF FACE=arial>
<P>I dont see why you people insist on ruining the setting of some awesome pvping and plot, because roleplaying on the pvp server is so freaking easy. All it consists of is a few Ayes Nays, dont loot your race, help your race, and fight the opposing race without calling them a fag or bitch. Thats all! not hard to do .. by doing what ive mentioned above, you are playing your race, powergaming, roleplaying, pking and not messing up game, all at the same time. Just give it a try .. id hate to see the beautiful landscapes, mobs, and all of the other wonderful things on the server be ruined because everyone is too stupid and lazy to play there race and not use bad language.

</FONT></td></tr></table></P>
